#- §lChapter 1: The§0
§0§l Grestin Expansion§0
§0Grestin (or Draconis) was a smaller nation owned by Komarni, the three leaders were 1234fireball, Freddo3000, and Jabbe00. their main city was in the jungle and was isolated, the Grestin Expansion was a mass
#- cutting of trees and territory§0
§0
§0§lChapter 2: The §0
§0 §0§lRebellion of§0
§0§l §0§lGrestin§0
§01234fireball was a communist through and through, so the democracy type style of Grestin was not a fit for him. He tried changing the system§0

#- to fit his needs, but it ended up with his leadership terminated and him pearled. A plan ensued to rescue 1234fireball. It was successful, and in turn they created a camp West of Grestin to prepare for an invasion of Grestin.
#- I, Creeperassassin_, got word of this and informed their leaders immediately, and in turn, they launched an invasion of the camp, destroying it completely. The civil war was flaming.§0

#- §lChapter 3: A birth§0
§0§l of a new nation§0
§0§lAn area south of Brandywine and east of Germany, was now created and called Chernarus. They set up to escape their actions far south, at the time, it mainly consisted of a large windmill, a temple, and camp tents.§0

#- §lChapter 4:§0
§0§l Burning of§0
§0§l Chernarus.§0
§0Chernarus had seemingly forgot that the Civil War was alive and well. So, as an act of the Civil War, I decided to launch an unauthorized attack and put the nail in the coffin of Chernarus. I ventured far.
#- Once I reached the destination, a quick battle ensued. Diamonds vs stone made it quick, as Grestin won. Everything was burned and torched to symbolize never to mess with Grestin again.§0

#- §lChapter 5: The§0
§0§l Trial of Creeper§0
§0The burning of Chernarus caused large controversy. On one side, I was a terrorist, on the other, it was a act of the Civil War and acceptable. The conclusion? It was a act of the Civil War,
#- and I was let free with a fine.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 6:§0
§0§l Annexation§0
§0§l of Germany§0
§0Chernarus, who was power hungry, annexed the nearest, largest, and least active state, Germany.
#- Most were in favor of it, recognizing their claim, and so the land was theirs.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 7:§0
§0§l Chernarus§0
§0§l To CSSR.§0
§0Chernarus was the name of their capital, so to represent the new land, the nation was renamed to CSSR.§0

#- §lChapter 8: The§0
§0§l Annexation of New§0
§0§l Wales.§0
§0New Wales was a nearby nation, and with the success of the last claim, they decided to grab more territory. However, New Wales was very active. The excuse was that their capital was built in their
#- land. This was heavily debated and denied. So in order to get the land they wanted, a war started.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 9: War§0
§0§l of New Wales§0
§0§l & Anschluss.§0
§0The war was fought for the tip of New Wales. However, it was 
#- short lived as 1234fireball called off the attack before it escalated into a larger issue.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 10:§0
§0§l A short peace.§0
§0This was a quick amount of time where everything was peaceful in the region, and anything
#- that would've happened, didn't. But as stated before, it was short lived.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 11: Birth§0
§0§l of a Civil War§0
§0CSSR at the time, was going through large political reform. New ideas were being thrown around. The ones that was kept 
#- were Roman Ideals. Diamondx10, the 2nd leader, was heavily opposed to the idea from changing the heavily communist nation to Roman, and stated his beliefs. 1234fireball was dead set on Roman, while Diamond was set on Communism. Since neither of them could
#- come to a compromise, a battle commenced. neither side won, but it was clear - a civil war had begun. Diamondx10 had gathered a gang of men and forced 1234fireball to give them the northern half of the territory.
#- §lChapter 12:§0
§0§l North vs. South§0
§01234fireball owned the Capital of CSSR, while diamond owned some forests to the North East. Diamondx10 wanted full control, and pushed foward. gaining land after land until eventually 1234fireball was
#- pushed back to the city of Chernarus.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 13: Battle§0
§0§l of Chernarus§0
§0The battle of Chernarus happened in minutes, buildings were destroyed and flamed. The battle ended shortly, as 1234fireball had killed and captured 
#- Diamondx10. This signaled that the end of the war was in sight.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 14:§0
§0§l A New Visitor§0
§0The return of me. Relations had settled and I was now a firework trader, making and selling explosive eye candy 
#- to anyone willing to buy it. I set up shop in Chernarus, but soon after I realized that a Civil War was on, and that it was happening in the very city I was in. So, to escape it, I fled to Brandywine to set up shop there. All the while being called a
#- traitor by 1234fireball for not staying open in the war ravaged city.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 15:  A §0
§0§l False Hope & The§0
§0§l End of the War§0
§0The false hope was that once the war was finished and diamondx10 pearled, 1234fireball turned 
#- the roman ideals into a more rogue version of Communism. he promised roman ideals and a peaceful nation, but he failed to give both. The only good side? The war was finally over.§0

#- §lChapter 16: A New §0
§0§l Enemy.§0
§0A group of 3, Jacob, Eran_von_baron, and Meeplewood, hated the CSSR and were old citizens of them. They visited Brandywine, talking of the hatred, when our paths met. We had a plan to take down the CSSR. It spanned 2
#- days, with regular attacks coming up. The plan was to have Meeple, Jacob, and Baron attack the city at different times to weaken it. Chests were destroyed, and buildings were bombed. Then, the final part of our plan came into action - the Siege of CSSR.§0

#- §lChapter 17: Siege§0
§0§l of CSSR§0
§0The plan was to have me bait 1234fireball to come online and have Meeple waiting by him. Jacob wanted a piece of land to the east, a small mushroom island, so that was our bait. Once he and his inner crew came on, Meeple
#- and Baron slayed them all. The ambush we had planned was successful. 1234fireball and the rest were pearled and were awaiting to be sold away.§0

#- §lChapter 18:§0
§0§l Death of CSSR.§0
§0§lThe city was torn apart, and would serve as a reminder to not only to not mess with us, but to show as history to the Communist vermin.§0

#- §lChapter 19:§0
§0§l A New Nation§0
§0A nation was birthed in the ashes of CSSR. The nation was called Meeples Wood, and would keep the land safe from any left over Communist fighters. The new nation planned to split the land up among other nations like New 
#- Wales and Lakeheart. The rogue nation was finally destroyed.§0
§0
§0-------------------§0

#- §lHistory after CSSR:§0
§0
§0§lChapter 20: Fort §0
§0§l Merryweather§0
§0The nation was small, and needed to defend itself, so a fort made of stone bricks and cobble was constructed on the hillside with a large tower overlooking Old-CSSR, the valley, 
#- and the nearby road.§0
§0
§0§lChapter 21: The§0
§0§l Red Wedding§0
§0Baron and I, two people who had loved each other for a very long time, decided it was time for marriage. The wedding was held at none other than Fort Merryweather.
#- It was decorated to the brim. Cakes were placed. Fireworks were set. The wedding would be beautiful. Once it started, everything went great... until the assassination. Right after the fireworks were set off and a speech was given, one bow shot to my head 
#- killed me. It started a fight and a large killing attempt of everyone by everyone. There were few casualties. Thieves came in and stole horses and gifts, but they were eventually killed. The Red Wedding will symbolize the attack on a peaceful event.
